/2025/02/David-Tennant-Donald-Trump-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/David-Tennant-Donald-Trump-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/David-Tennant-Donald-Trump-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/bafta">BAFTA</a>电影奖主持人<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/david-tennant">大卫·坦南特（David Tennant）</a>开玩笑说<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/donald-trump">美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）</a>从周日晚上（2月16日）电视台广播中裁员。在现场仪式上，他将政治家与Beetlejuice的性格进行了比较。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/here-are-all-the-winners-from-the-baftas-2025-3838432">这是BAFTA 2025的所有获奖者</a></strong></li></ul><p>编辑是在一个笑话中开玩笑的，从<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/the-brutalist"><em>野蛮主义者</em></a>开始。 “这是今年电影中最大胆的建筑，除了唐纳德·特朗普在<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/the-apprentice"><em>学徒</em></a>中的头发外，这是他的笑话，这确实使它播出了。</p><p>不包括以下内容：“唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump），他说他没有看过<em>学徒，</em>因为这是15（电影的评分）。它不在Nickelodeon上。唐纳德·特朗普...我很担心。我说过他的名字三遍。就像Beetlejuice一样 - 我召唤了他。”取而代之的是，编辑从关于特朗普的头发的讽刺到坦南特说“谈论小人……”，并向<em>诺斯费拉图</em>和<em>异端</em>撰写了一篇文章。</p><p>这个笑话很可能是在时间而不是争议的，因为该节目通常会在电视上进行三个小时的运行时间中的三分之一。 BAFTA广播<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/bbc">公司</a>在给<a href="https://variety.com/2025/film/awards/david-tennant-trump-beetlejuice-joke-cut-bbc-baftas-broadcast-1236310226/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Variety</em></a>的一份声明中说：“该节目的性质是它的延迟延迟了，并且由于时间限制而必须进行编辑”。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="大卫·坦南特（David Tennant）的开场独白和歌曲！ 🎭| BAFTA电影奖2025" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/uXdWCVKbLF4?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> The biggest night in the British film industry saw <a href="https://www.nme.com/films/conclave"><em>Conclave</em></a> and <em>The Brutalist</em> win four awards each – the former taking Best Picture, Adapted Screenplay, Editing and Outstanding British Film and the latter winning Best Director, Actor for Adrien Brody, Score and Cinematography.</p><p> As well as Tennant&#39;s joke, <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/zoe-saldana">Zoe Saldaña&#39;s</a> acceptance speech after winning Best Supporting Actress for <a href="https://www.nme.com/films/emilia-perez"><em>Emilia Pérez</em></a> was <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/heres-what-zoe-saldana-actually-said-in-her-censored-baftas-speech-3838498">cut from the broadcast</a> . The director of <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kneecap"><em>Kneecap</em></a> , Rich Peppiatt, dedicated his BAFTA Film Award to “everyone out there” who is fighting to <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/kneecap-director-dedicates-bafta-to-everyone-who-should-have-their-homeland-respected-3838475">“have their homeland respected”.</a></p><p> The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/heres-david-tennants-donald-trump-joke-that-the-bbc-cut-from-bafta-broadcast-3838603">Here&#39;s David Tennant&#39;s Donald Trump joke that the BBC cut from BAFTA broadcast</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
